      "startTime": 17.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1111327013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　マズいな。予約したタクシーが渋滞に捕まって\n来られないみたいです。新しいのを探さないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? This is bad. The taxi we reserved is caught in traffic\nand can't come. We need to find a new one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8552.3602984,
          "startTime": 31.4856936317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら電車を乗り継いで行きましょう\nほら、急ぎなさい、走るわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let's take the train with transfers.\nCome on‚ hurry up‚ we're running!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9666678111,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.3321889,
          "startTime": 34.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7989566645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい、莉央さん\n速過ぎます、追いつけませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a moment‚ Rio-san.\nYou're too fast‚ I can't keep up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9103640081
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
