      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私達が星見プロに移籍する時――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ when we transferred to Hoshimi Pro――",
